{"tid":1484322,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今次港共中共班垃圾唔知又會作咩故仔呢","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:36:19.000Z","uid":20559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef5e1ba7fd1db8ccd94267f5db902e5daa3dff6d","tid":1484322,"uid":20559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"共狗又口口聲聲話香港示威係港獨又頻色革命乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n港共仲好笑真係派粒糖比我咁大把以為可以叫人收聲<br />\n<br />\n香港人未撚見過你幾千蚊咩<br />\n<br />\n之前預算案叫你還富於民又唔撚理<br />\n<br />\n而家搞到咁大鑊比粒豆我想我哽死？<br />\n<br />\n賣港賣到億億聲送上大陸當香港人盲嘅？<br />\n<br />\n而家真係唔知佢可以點兜啦<br />\n<br />\n香港係咪有二百萬人遊行支持顏色革命呀？<br />\n<br />\n真係頭痕啦，唯有當睇唔到算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4ce48fc12706dafcb7c421d51ceab7cefd3f49","tid":1484322,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:32:13.000Z","msg":"[香港淡奶] 屬於香港人嘅Timeline上線喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a23eff9700ea9648154fde43d86982706ac6779f","tid":1484322,"uid":20559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n一齊諗下佢哋會點講<br />\n<br />\n咪扮睇唔到啦<br />\n<br />\n柒到應一應"}]}